In celebration of Hispanic Heritage Month, join us for our next Pipeline Panel on Thursday, September 28 at 5:00 p.m. as we discuss the Hispanic experience within the professional baseball landscape. 

The call will feature Giants Manager Gabe Kapler, Forever Giant Pablo Sandoval, Giants Infielder Wilmer Flores, Giants Quality Assurance Coach Nick Ortiz, Giants Assistant Hitting Coach Pedro Guerrero and Pipeline for Change Executive Director Stephanie St Amour.

Sandoval is a 2x MLB All-Star and 3x World Series Champion. Sandoval has collected 1200+ hits and 150+ HRs in Major League Baseball.
